HEADWORD: Transvolation
<hw>Trans`vo*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>transvolare</ets> to fly over or across; <ets>trans</ets> across +
<ets>volare</ets> to fly.]</ety> <def>The act of flying beyond or
across.</def> <rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
